    (18,'Bosnian American Islamic Center','3437 Caniff Street Hamtramck, MI','(313) 893-685','NULL','Bosnian','NULL','10/18/1995','1998','NULL','NULL','NULL','The Bosniak American Islamic Center began its work in 1998. The primary goal is to preserve Islam and Bosniak identity, culture and tradition.','7.21576E+16','https://www.facebook.com/BAIC-Detroit-117926154972231/','NULL','https://cofs.lara.state.mi.us/CorpWeb/CorpSearch/CorpSummary.aspx?ID=800815264&SEARCH_TYPE=1','NULL'),
